{"tid":644321,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"蝻亞狗恰阿婆","createTime":"2018-04-27T07:14:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-27T07:14:25.000Z","uid":136455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"78d1884a8e14f4fafc70f79a0df6df71eef41fb6","tid":644321,"uid":136455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T07:14:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180426/bkn-20180426184243539-0426_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180426%2Fbkn-20180426184243539-0426_00822_001.html&d=qGy8gEYPqsXYxjpZAllIv8PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=934dc8b2\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180426/bkn-20180426184243539-0426_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n南亞兵團犯案不絕，爆樽扑頭傷人逃去。下午5時許，一名姓吳(68歲)老婦在大角咀道38號新九龍廣場停車場附近通道，推着手推車為其他車輛抹車期間，一名南亞裔男子突從後撲出，並用玻璃樽扑向老婦，致其頭部受傷流血，兇徒得逞後隨即逃去。<br />\n<br />\n有駕駛人士途經現場見狀，立即上前協助老婦並報警。老婦遇襲後仍然清醒，由救護員敷治後送院治理。據悉，遇襲老婦已在上址從事抹車工作逾10年，惟近日有南亞幫向她出言恐嚇，聲稱要接手其抹車工作，警方正根據附近閉路電視片段，追緝涉案南亞漢。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/27/151422_44e99b889976019fcecabcd344c6e4d3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F27%2F151422_44e99b889976019fcecabcd344c6e4d3.jpg&h=ca1063a3&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}